<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <style>
        body { font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333; max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px; }
        .header { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1e3a8a, #2563eb); color: white; padding: 40px; border-radius: 12px 12px 0 0; text-align: center; }
        .content { background: #ffffff; padding: 40px; border: 1px solid #e5e7eb; border-radius: 0 0 12px 12px; box-shadow: 0 4px 6px -1px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1); }
        .footer { text-align: center; font-size: 12px; color: #6b7280; margin-top: 30px; }
        .feature-card { background: #f8fafc; padding: 20px; border-radius: 8px; margin: 20px 0; border-left: 4px solid #2563eb; }
        .btn { display: inline-block; background: #2563eb; color: white; padding: 14px 28px; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 6px; font-weight: bold; margin-top: 20px; box-shadow: 0 2px 4px rgba(37, 99, 235, 0.3); }
        h1 { margin: 0; font-size: 28px; letter-spacing: -0.5px; }
        h2 { color: #1e3a8a; margin-top: 0; }
        .accent { color: #2563eb; font-weight: bold; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="header">
        <h1>Welcome to Bank Inner Core</h1>
    </div>
    <div class="content">
        <h2>Hello {{name}},</h2>
        <p>Welcome to the future of digital banking. We're excited to have you join our community of forward-thinking members.</p>
        
        <div class="feature-card">
            <p><strong>What's Next?</strong></p>
            <ul style="padding-left: 20px; margin: 10px 0;">
                <li>Set up your <span class="accent">Multi-Factor Authentication</span> for peak security.</li>
                <li>Explore our <span class="accent">Smart Vaults</span> for goal-based savings.</li>
                <li>Monitor transactions in <span class="accent">Real-time</span> with AI-powered tracking.</li>
            </ul>
        </div>

        <p>Your journey towards financial excellence starts today. Log in now to explore your new dashboard.</p>
        
        <div style="text-align: center;">
            <a href="#" class="btn">Get Started Now</a>
        </div>

        <p style="margin-top: 30px; font-size: 14px; color: #64748b;">If you didn't create this account, please ignore this email or contact support.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="footer">
        &copy; 2026 Bank Inner Core. All rights reserved.<br>
        123 Financial District, Tech City.
    </div>
</body>
</html>
